folder: Bridge Street & York Street, Brooklyn, NY
text:
97 Bridge Street, at the N.E. corner of York Street, showing also the Brooklyn Union Gas Co. tank on York Street. No. 2 shows the frame
building at the corner demolished.
November 1, 1927.
View 2: April 5, 1938.
P. L. Sperr.
